**CIA Classification:** Salary requires HIGH confidentiality (restricted access, encryption at rest/in transit), HIGH integrity (audit trails, change controls, tamper detection), and MEDIUM availability (non-critical but essential for payroll). **GDPR Classification:** Salary is personal data requiring lawful basis (typically employment contract). It qualifies as special category data when combined with employment records, triggering enhanced protections. Subject to data subject rights (access, rectification, erasure, portability) and mandatory data minimization. Retention limited to employment duration plus statutory requirements (typically 3-7 years). Processing requires DPA clauses with third parties and privacy impact assessment for any new uses.
